info.description:
PySPM has moved to pycroscopy (https://pypi.python.org/pypi/pyCroscopy/ and https://pycroscopy.github.io/pycroscopy/)

A suite of utilities for image processing and scientific analysis of scanning probe microscopy data.
SPM methods supported: Multi-frequency electromechanical and force microscopy, Scanning Tunneling microscopy.
info.name: pySPM
info.summary: Python Library for I/O, processing, and analysis of scanning probe microscopy data.
